reviews: For those wondering about the authenticity of these beanies, here's a clarification. If you do a quick google search, you will find that there are two branches to Carhartt: Classic Carhartt (workers wear) and Carhartt WIP (Work In Progress) which is the streetwear line. This is a classic Carhartt beanie hence the low price, it is not a "fake". The Carhartt WIP beanies are a bit higher quality and go for about 30$. In my pictures, you can see the difference between the the two, Classic Carhartt on the right and Carhartt WIP on the left.
Great size, can fit in your pocket no problem. I use it everyday to keep my phone alive, it can fully charge my galaxy S7 at least twice.
